	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">高端旅行兴起，这种生活方式可以给品牌带来多少机会？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-18 07:35:30 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">2</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">28</span>
		</div>
